&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current State RN license&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPR/AED certification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong clinical assessment and care planning skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective leadership, coaching, and team development abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Preferred:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RAC Certification and/or demonstrated MDS/PPS reimbursement experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of ICD-10 coding and regulatory requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior&amp;nbsp;nurse&amp;nbsp;management or supervisory experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum two years of MDS and geriatric nursing experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
